purpose: The email is a call for workshop proposals for the IEEE International Conference on Artificial Intelligence of Things (IEEE AIoT 2025), scheduled for December 3-5, 2025, in Osaka, Japan. It also includes an apology for any duplicate messages received regarding this call for proposals.
